data.description: This meticulously crafted home, upgraded beyond its original design, offers a warm embrace with 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a study, loft, formal dining area, and a 2-car garage.Laundry thoughtfully placed on the same floor as most bedrooms with additional hookup in the lower level, walk-in closets and ample storage space throughout the home.  But the real surprise lies below, where a finished basement awaits, complete with an extra bedroom, spacious family room and office area overlooking the Blue Ridge Mountains.  The screened in deck or concrete patio provide the perfect retreat for relaxation or entertaining guests. Convenience to all your Roanoke shopping and restaurant needs, and the natural beauty that surrounds it. It's a place where you can create memories, come see it today!
